{"tid":171242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政治光譜已重新劃分為︰西環建制派﹑中環建制派﹑本土自決港獨","createTime":"2017-03-25T07:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T17:27:37.000Z","uid":38671,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32512ba2ddf9e29e4e9753e76662d2992aada4c7","tid":171242,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"無論特首選舉結果係點，香港政治光譜已重新劃分為︰<br />\n<br />\n西環建制派︰<br />\n以西環勢力為首既建制派<br />\n<br />\n中環建制派︰<br />\n唔妥西環建制派既建制派。加上黃絲異變，揭開追求民主外皮，實際擁護建制。<br />\n<br />\n本土自決港獨︰<br />\n不用分那麼細，西環建制派認為全部都係港獨，中環建制派認為全部都係政治白痴或者係鬼。"},{"pid":"0081b80cfd2836578f02a5dcfd608989329658bd","tid":171242,"uid":45473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"中環建制派 黃絲異變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec223907e7c99f6d184cbd147d01ea110627fee","tid":171242,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"奧士本准尉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc490b8a9f94fb0a8f78cd4bba9ca9140ce59a9","tid":171242,"uid":39572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"原來敵人一直在自己身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b201933cb406f99f7245a1ffc1ae3816ea333a","tid":171242,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"你地無去HKU 個CE forum, 仆佢個街, <br />\n成班泛民大狀呀、律師, 笑得好開心架<br />\n<br />\n但又何須咁驚訝或失望呢？<br />\n就係泛民黃絲豬不嬲都仆街, 唔打算靠佢地, <br />\n我地呢幾年先會港獨呀！<br />\n<br />\n唔係well expected咩？將來港獨, 都唔會受呢班廢人影響架啦！<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\nHKU 個CE forum,, 早走返屋企同囡囡啪啪啪...<br />\n費事浪費生命聽廢話, 見到泛民廢人就嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/hxtypvid5/CE_Forum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fhxtypvid5%2FCE_Forum.jpg&h=57eb3f01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c33839c572652284cd3acaf69e5188e5ef98c288","tid":171242,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"林鄭贏︰黃絲異變既中環建制派會扮返民主派，但底牌已被睇穿<br />\n<br />\n薯片贏︰西環勢力減弱，部份黃絲異變既中環建制派會正式成為建制打手"},{"pid":"5b13d90cb0d9336d41e050577273369407aecfbb","tid":171242,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f7fc956a00e09aca5da22805d0fd508127bb93","tid":171242,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49218a78bf04073cc0b90276bd80bb2b539b3007","tid":171242,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"咁分法<br />\n仲有幾多人撐港獨"},{"pid":"419513beaefab9ce6129abc85760899b5a131e78","tid":171242,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T17:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}